TileWorld
    getTileSize -> 32
    getWidth    -> Nbr of horizontal tiles
    getHeight
    also encapsulates mapSymbolToTerreinType

Camera manages the viewport and renders the map
    setFocus(x, y) makes sure that given position is closest to the centre as possible
    setViewportSize / -position
    setTileWorld

rud as thing in game world:  location or eventful object.
ruds can be placed independent of the map grid.

player counts as a special kind of rud, which is default  rudOfInterest ie thing the camera is tracking.
